-- GM skids 24 percent after S&P statement
-- 
-- Thu Oct 9, 2008 3:46pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/09/us-markets-stocks-gm-idUSTRE49888S20081009

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of General Motors Corp ,a Dow component, slid more than 24 percent to $5.32 in afternoon trade on Thursday as credit rating agency Standard & Poor's said it may cut the automaker's long-term credit rating. 

 (Reporting by  Ellis Mnyandu ; Editing by Leslie Adler)